@startuml
title Read/List Process (Level 1) — VendNet

actor "Actor\n(Customer/Operator/Admin)" as User
participant "VendNet System" as System

User -> System: Request data listing / item details
activate System
System -> System: Validate request parameters
alt Parameters are valid
    System -> System: Fetch data
    System -> System: Apply filtering and sorting
    System --> User: Display list of items / item details
else Parameters are invalid
    System --> User: Display error message (Invalid parameters)
end
deactivate System
@enduml